-- Yemen Car Bombing Kills Security Official in Hadramaut Province
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 2012-08-10T01:06:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-10/yemen-car-bombing-kills-security-official-in-hadramaut-province.html
A senior Yemeni security official
was killed late yesterday in a car bomb attack in the
southeastern province city of Mukalla, the state-run Saba news
agency reported today.  Brigadier Omar Barasheed, dean of the Command and General
Staff College, was killed when a bomb hidden inside the car
exploded in Mukalla, the capital of Hadramaut province. He died
in the hospital.  His bodyguard was also killed and his son wounded in the
blast, according to al-Masdar, a local independent news website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
